{"type": "article", "id": 17914, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-11-23T06:58:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 19134, "name": "KANARI"}, {"id": 19135, "name": "滨文样"}, {"id": 332, "name": "百威"}, {"id": 19136, "name": "Johan Kauppi"}, {"id": 19137, "name": "Bertil Harström"}, {"id": 19138, "name": "Rachel Harding"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122428XTpigvqCh1VNaGxP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tHarass furniture collection by Johan Kauppi &amp; Bertil Hagström \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是瑞典设计师 Johan Kauppi 和 Bertil Harström 合作的户外家具系列。在长条胶合集成木板下配上黄色的钢管作为支撑，可以调节高低，安插在户外的地面上能保持平衡，也方便更换。厚重的木质材料几乎遮盖了短小的黄色钢管，让这组家具有悬浮感，显得轻盈。不同的类型可以相互组成户外桌椅或高低相错的长椅，而最大的木框是一个为户外游玩的人提供庇护的地方。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214907SN40PYi6Uvykt7hB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214908vGe8yYhAoc5ZPIsl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214908gxfVwkjJYR2Gv7Kc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214908MmtZF5yKlUa3EoJ4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214909DAqklFXnGP2N9hr1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214909LHnKJwr8o46pFNqY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t横滨捺染 by 滨文样\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t滨文样是日本横滨的传统手巾品牌，将一块大的手巾像书一样叠起来，用红色棉线缝合成册，做成了手巾书，大小如同一个口袋本。每一种手巾都是通过横滨捺染的技法制作，是日式传统纹样和配色，很典雅。翻开每一页都是一个主题的不同样式，有很强的故事性。完全拆开后可以用来做桌布或者包裹物品。售价 130 元，<a href=\"http://s.taobao.com/search?q=%E6%BB%A8%E6%96%87%E6%A0%B7+%E6%A8%AA%E6%BB%A8%E6%8D%BA%E6%9F%93+%E6%96%87%E5%BA%93&amp;js=1&amp;stats_click=search_radio_all%3A1&amp;initiative_id=staobaoz_20151122&amp;ie=utf8\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214910dwkPlJn9L1AXVU26.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214910bsm0QrcX16FWRqPU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214911f5CS8IP6v0OaW3e2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214911ziSE473vFXxfZAqr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214912aUX7S8vzbm3opTxd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tKANARI collection by <span>KANARI </span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自台湾的设计事务所 KANARI 带来的家用产品系列，包括灯具，时钟和开瓶器。共同点在于每一系列都有金、银、铜三种带有金属感的颜色，线条简明清晰，有古典式的优雅和现代气息。其中，挂钟像套在了几个圆环里，大小圆环的阴影通过灯光投射在墙面上，很有艺术感。目前时钟和开瓶器已可出售，<a href=\"http://www.studiokanari.com/#!shop/ccnu\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214913dDkX2MVJifLI5ytc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.54444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214913o7zW01Mvrk8AcfCj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214914xXvzDB9dVimqnJa7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052149146P1CL82EsZFabRYI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052149159tXmOKJCW1Zq0QgE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214915m7xNb3vlFAJBWsRj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tDorian chair by Rachel Harding\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是伦敦设计师 Rachel Harding 带来“充气椅”，实际上是将空气充进了可耐力材料里，让椅子可以像花岗岩一样坚固。在高温下，可耐力材料可以变得很柔软，填进空气后有气球的膨胀感，冷却后又重新变成坚固的材料。Rachel Harding 使用了三维建模软件设计了这款充满未来感的椅子，也是对材料的新探索。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214916RW2C8DpQsKedriS5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214916Hpd6QPb82WyecMFo.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052149171CWUqmtIpuK5z3ZP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521491749sGbDB2fFCIWOeq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214918xVbwP4UO9qkCKWD1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSabbatical Travel Kit by Timbuk2 &amp; Blue Bottle\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款专放咖啡制作器具的帆布包，为那些喜欢自制咖啡且有移动需要的人提供。帆布包的外形方正，近似一个旅行包，打开后可以看到已划分好的格子，可以放置一套咖啡器皿，包括去毛刺的咖啡研磨机、滴水计时器、来自日本的烧水壶、两个珐琅杯等，售价 349 美元，<a href=\"http://www.timbuk2.com/blue-bottle-sabbatical-travel-kit/581.html?dwvar_581_color=1920&amp;dwvar_581_size=10&amp;utm_source=EEAN-21181&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2-223763&amp;utm_content=1449174793&amp;utm_term=skim77721X1528342Xc181123aedcc0e46906fd9d97aa48c21\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214918NeGSfTQu95pqBivA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214919Zn6viBAGfRyPTeOk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.803125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214919dnFJ9PvzB2KRUpgE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214920Y5iywHUNAcEd9Lg4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214920lb0w1r32FsIBENpL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tBud Light cans by Daniel Triendl\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t百威清啤 Bud Light 为了今年的 Mad Decent Block Party，邀请奥地利设计师 Daniel Triendl 设计了一组限量版的易拉罐。罐身可见用油画式的笔触书写的线条或字母，厚重且含有丰富的颜色，显得张扬大胆，契合年轻人。或者使用像素化的图像，在颜色的撞击中带来一种时尚感。<a href=\"http://danieltriendl.com/Bud-Light-Mad-Decent-Block-Party\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214921PXRCGAu3seagdo01.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214921gnuX05VaLQoDsqb2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214922hM3Xf2iYR7bgyNln.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214922dGrc5xwk7QEaU8Bq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.744\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052149231egOZyxTCfv2MUoB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605214923WUqNvpf5XJ8Qod2a.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.13240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}